source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
<p>A line of only pipes is plain text, never a table:</p>
<p>|</p>
<p>||</p>
<p>|||</p>
<p>A table stops at a following pipe-only line:</p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><p>a</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>|</p>
<p>A pipe-only line before a table stays a paragraph:</p>
<p>|</p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><p>b</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
